BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:fKJj-hwAOlWae8Qg-s5je
SUMMARY:Show Your Game: An Improvised Game Show
DTSTAMP:20260307T065917Z
DTSTART:20260308T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Sundays in March! A Comedy Game Show About Ridiculously Specifi
	c Expertise. Everyone is secretly an expert at something. In Show Your Gam
	e \, professional improvisers and fearless audience volunteers step into t
	he worlds of real-life experts and attempt to survive challenges designed 
	by those experts. Expect strange trivia\, impossible tasks\, wildly specif
	ic knowledge\, and the kind of confidence that only comes from being compl
	etely wrong in public. Maybe it’s acupuncture. Maybe it’s panic packing. M
	aybe it’s Gilmore Girls . Maybe it’s finding creative new places to lose y
	our keys. Inspired by the chaotic brilliance of Taskmaster \, the clever c
	uriosity of QI \, and the unpredictable madness of Game Changer \, every s
	how is completely improvised and completely different. Past topics have in
	cluded haunting\, bubbles\, bedtime routines\, public art\, computer progr
	amming\, low-income housing\, tabletop RPG streaming\, Veggie Tales\, hous
	esitting disasters\, and one unforgettable investigation into a s\n\nhttps
	://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/show-your-game-an-improvised-ga
	me-show-2/?occurrence=2026-03-08\n\nFrom Pike Place Market Events
URL:https://www.pikeplacemarket.org/events-calendar/show-your-game-an-impro
	vised-game-show-2/?occurrence=2026-03-08
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:events
CATEGORIES:Pike Place Market Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
